==Korean==
===Adverb===
'''대단히''' (dae.dan.hi)
#very (much), so (much), extremely, exceedingly
#대단히 고맙습니다 ('''''daedanhi''' gomapsupnida'') Thank you '''very much''' / Thank you '''so much''' 
#언니는 대단히 부진런하다. (''eonnineun daedanhi bujinreonhada'') [My] big sister is very hardworking. 

